object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT basicpolicy_stg.SystemId,basicpolicy_stg.Id, basicpolicy_stg.PolicyNumber, basicpolicy_stg.StatusCd, basicpolicy_stg.CarrierCd,basicpolicy_stg.TransactionCd,basicpolicy_stg.InceptionDt, basicpolicy_stg.EffectiveDt, basicpolicy_stg.ExpirationDt, basicpolicy_stg.CancelDt, case when len(basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)
             when len(basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)
             else basicpolicy_stg.policyversion end as policyversion, basicpolicy_stg.QuoteNumber, basicpolicy_stg.ProviderRef,basicpolicy_stg.ApplicationNumber,basicpolicy_stg.ManualRenewalInd,basicpolicy_stg.ProgramCd,basicpolicy_stg.Tier,basicpolicy_stg.PayPlanCd,basicpolicy_stg.InspectionOrderedDt, basicpolicy_stg.SubTypeCd
,basicpolicy_stg.ControllingStateCd,basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd, basicpolicy_stg.RenewalPolicyRef
,basicpolicy_stg.IsMigrated
,Insured_stg.InspectionContact
,Insured_stg.InspectionContactNumber
,emailinfo_stg.EmailAddr, 
CASE 
          WHEN cs.carriercd IS NULL OR cs.carriercd = ''
          THEN basicpolicy_stg.CarrierCd 
           ELSE cs.carriercd 
 END as shell_carrier_cd
FROM
 dbo.basicpolicy_stg  basicpolicy_stg 
 LEFT JOIN dbo.Insured_stg Insured_stg  ON basicpolicy_stg.SystemId = Insured_stg.SystemId AND basicpolicy_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND Insured_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd IS NULL
LEFT JOIN dbo.emailinfo_stg emailinfo_stg ON basicpolicy_stg.SystemId = emailinfo_stg.SystemId
  AND basicpolicy_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND emailinfo_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd IS NULL
  AND emailinfo_stg.EmailTypeCd = 'InsuredEmail'
left join dbo.claimstats_stg cs
 on basicpolicy_stg.SystemId = cs.policyref

object.customQuery: SELECT transactionhistory.TransactionDt as TransactionDt, transactionhistory.SystemId as SystemId, transactionhistory.ParentId as ParentId FROM transactionhistory where TransactionCd='New Business' and  CMMContainer='Policy'
SELECT policy.CustomerRef as CustomerRef, policy.SystemId as SystemId FROM policy where cmmcontainer='Policy'

SELECT transactionhistory.TransactionCd as TransactionCd, transactionreason.ReasonCd as ReasonCd, basicpolicy.SystemId as SystemId, basicpolicy.PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber, basicpolicy.PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion from basicpolicy
 left join (select * from transactionhistory where transactionhistory.cmmcontainer = 'Policy')transactionhistory on basicpolicy.systemid = transactionhistory.systemid
 left join (select * from transactionreason where transactionreason.CMMContainer = 'Policy')transactionreason on transactionhistory.id = transactionreason.parentid
where basicpolicy.CMMContainer = 'Policy' and transactionhistory.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'  and transactionhistory.TransactionCd = 'Non Renewal'

object.name: policystats
object.customQuery:
SELECT policystats.CancelReason as CancelReason, 
policystats.CarrierCd as CarrierCd, 
policystats.PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber, 
policystats.PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion 
FROM policystats policystats  left join basicpolicy basicpolicy
 on policystats.policyref=basicpolicy.systemid
 and basicpolicy.cmmcontainer='Policy'
inner join (select policystats.policyref as policyref,
max(policystats.systemid) as maxsystemid from policystats policystats group by policyref) latest
on policystats.policyref=latest.policyref
and policystats.systemid =latest.maxsystemid
Where policystats.cancelreason is not null
or policystats.carriercd is not null

select PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber,PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion,RiskTypeCd as RiskTypeCd from (
select DISTINCT policystats.policynumber as PolicyNumber,policystats.policyversion as PolicyVersion ,policystats.RiskTypeCd as  RiskTypeCd 
from dbo.policystats_stg policystats  left join dbo.basicpolicy_Stg basicpolicy
 on policystats.policyref=basicpolicy.systemid
 and basicpolicy.cmmcontainer='Policy'
inner join (select policystats.policyref as policyref,max(policystats.systemid) as maxsystemid from dbo.policystats_stg policystats 
where policystats.RisktypeCd is not null
group by policyref) latest
on policystats.policyref=latest.policyref
and policystats.systemid =latest.maxsystemid
union
select distinct lp.PolicyNumber,lp.PolicyVersion  ,pt.RiskTypeCd from 
( Select t1.PolicyKey,t1.Risktypecd from dbo.PolicyTransaction t1 inner join  
(Select PolicyKey,max(StatSequence) as MaxStatSequence from dbo.PolicyTransaction
where RisktypeCd is not null
group by PolicyKey)t2 on t1.StatSequence=t2.MaxStatSequence)PT inner join dbo.Lkp_Policy lp
on pt.PolicyKey=lp.PolicyKey
inner join dbo.basicpolicy_stg stg on lp.PolicyNumber=stg.PolicyNumber
left join dbo.PolicyStats_Stg tstg on tstg.PolicyRef=stg.SystemId
where tstg.PolicyNumber is NULL
)t

fields.name: PolicyForm
fields.expression:
IIF(IN(v_TypeCD,'BOP', 'BOP1'), 'Standard',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'BOP2', 'Special',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'ExcessLiability' OR v_TypeCD='Businessowners Excess Liability', 'Excess',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'UmbrellaLiability' OR  v_TypeCD='Businessowners Umbrella Liability','Commercial Umbrella',

fields.name: StatusDesc
fields.expression:
IIF(StatusCd='Non-Renewed' AND PolicyExpirationDt >= SYSDATE ,'Nonrenewed (inforce)',
IIF(StatusCd='Non-Renewed' AND PolicyExpirationDt < SYSDATE,'Nonrenewed (expired)',StatusCd))

object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct ltrim(rtrim(convert(BS.Tier, char(10)))) as Tier, 
BS.H107Ind as H107Ind,
BS.SystemId as SystemId
FROM Building  BS 
join advrxxchangedbeans advr
on BS.SystemId = advr.SystemId
and BS.CMMContainer = advr.CMMContainer
where BS.CMMContainer='Policy' and BS.Status='Active'
Order by SystemId, Tier, H107Ind --

object.customQuery:
SELECT transactionhistory.TransactionCd as TransactionCd,
       transactionhistory.SourceCd as SourceCd,
       transactionhistory.SystemId as SystemId
FROM transactionhistory
JOIN (
    SELECT systemid, 
           MIN(concat(transactiondt, ' ', transactiontm)) AS Min_TransactionDt
    FROM transactionhistory
    WHERE sourcecd IS NOT NULL
      AND cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
    GROUP BY systemid
) first_trans ON transactionhistory.Systemid = first_trans.Systemid
    AND concat(transactiondt, ' ', transactiontm) = Min_TransactionDt
